{
  "stem": "19518.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 493.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no water to wash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was nothing to cover yourself with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was nothing to help yourself with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You just had-- so nature had to take its course the way you were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we were led outside of that area onto the road, and the orchestra was playing Mendelssohn's March.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Perfect music, perfect musicians, and we had to walk in that gooey soil.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because Poland has very rich soil, and it's full of gook after a rain, after snow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's gooey.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had to walk to the tap of the music of that march.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That music I'll never forget as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were led into the 2B2.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was, for the next five months, that was my address.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] First I was in block 9.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was a Jewish blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was a holy terror.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She was a holy, holy, terror.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I've never seen anything like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I don't think that I ever met a human being that should be so miserable, rotten, unhappy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Yes, each one of us lost families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But she was a holy terror, especially-- I'll use a Hungarian expression, [HUNGARIAN], that's a Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the world was guilty of everything that happened to her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And she was just like a wild animal let out of the cage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She did not have the whip, but she had a stick in her hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we tried very hard not to be within her reach ever, ever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because whoever was within her reach, it was just amazing how she did not break bones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That the rage in her was incredible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were 13 on a bunk area, which had only boards.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
